2026-03-29T16:38:41.8584678Z               "message": "Add sanitized database export to About page\n\nAdds a download button on the About page that creates a sanitized copy\nof the SQLite database with OAuth tokens and email addresses removed.\nUses VACUUM INTO for a consistent snapshot, then sanitizes via direct\nSQLite UPDATE before serving. Includes concurrency guard and temp file\ncleanup.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01QYf6BWVswoLZy5dhjW8hrR",
